*Advisor and Featured Expert, Children's Television Workshop Web site{{Fact|date=February 2007}}
*Privacy and safety advisor to Disney Online's Internet safety project, http://surfswellisland.com
*Advisor and Contributor, GetNetWise{{Fact|date=February 2007}}
